2018年7月17日，[[Netflix|Netflix]]宣布已向該劇訂購了第一季共八集<ref name="SeriesOrder">{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/jupiters-legacy-series-empress-film-mark-millars-first-netflix-slate-1127578|title='Jupiter's Legacy' Series, 'Empress' Film Among Mark Millar's First Netflix Slate|last2=Goldberg|first2=Lesley|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=July 17, 2018|access-date=February 10, 2019|archive-date=December 24, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201224171735/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/jupiters-legacy-series-empress-film-mark-millars-first-netflix-slate-1127578|url-status=live}}</ref>。該劇由[[史蒂芬·S·迪奈特|史蒂芬·S·迪奈特]]開發，他與[[洛倫佐·迪·波納文圖拉|洛倫佐·迪·波納文圖拉]]和丹·麥達莫一起被認為是執行製作人<ref name="SeriesOrder" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://media.netflix.com/en/press-releases/netflix-announces-first-slate-of-series-and-films-based-on-the-stories-of-mark-millar|title=Netflix announces first slate of series and films based on the stories of Mark Millar|website=Netflix Media Center|date=July 17, 2018|access-date=February 10, 2019|archive-date=January 6, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200106010608/https://media.netflix.com/en/press-releases/netflix-announces-first-slate-of-series-and-films-based-on-the-stories-of-mark-millar|url-status=live}}</ref>。2019年9月16日，經證實，迪奈特在第一季的製作過程中因創作差異而離開本劇擔任[[節目統籌|節目統籌]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/09/jupiters-legacy-steven-s-deknight-exits-showrunner-filming-netflix-series-continues-1202735950/|title='Jupiter's Legacy': Showrunner Steven S. DeKnight Exits As Filming Of Netflix Series Continues|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=September 16, 2019|access-date=September 16, 2019|archive-date=September 17, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190917052429/https://deadline.com/2019/09/jupiters-legacy-steven-s-deknight-exits-showrunner-filming-netflix-series-continues-1202735950/|url-status=live}}</ref> 。2019年11月，在迪奈特退出本劇之後，宣布金相圭將接任節目統籌<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/11/jupiters-legacy-sang-kim-showrunner-netflix-series-steven-s-deknight-exit-1202781907/|title='Jupiter's Legacy': Sang Kim Joins As Showrunner Of Netflix Series Following Steven S. DeKnight Exit|last=Petski|first=Denise|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=November 8, 2019|access-date=December 5, 2019|archive-date=December 15, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191215155035/https://deadline.com/2019/11/jupiters-legacy-sang-kim-showrunner-netflix-series-steven-s-deknight-exit-1202781907/|url-status=live}}</ref>。
2021年5月9日，本劇原創[[馬克·米勒_(作家)|馬克·米勒]]向《Comicbook.com》網站透露對系列第二季以及外傳的潛在規劃，他表示「我們知道接下來要怎麼走，畢竟漫畫原著就是很好的範本。這些漫畫都放在那邊等著我們，所以我們有一個很粗略的計劃。但我們知道，一切都得視觀眾是否會作出我們所預期的反應，但我們對此很有信心。」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://comicbook.com/tv-shows/news/jupiters-legacy-season-2-spoilers-sequel-requiem-mark-millar/|title=Jupiter's Legacy Creator Mark Millar Teases Plans for Season 2 and Sequel Series|last=Schmidt|first=Joe|work=Comic Book|date=May 9, 2021|access-date=May 9, 2021|archive-date=2021-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210803132303/https://comicbook.com/tv-shows/news/jupiters-legacy-season-2-spoilers-sequel-requiem-mark-millar/|url-status=no}}</ref>。6月2日，據報導，由於演員陣容已經發布，本劇將不會是繼續進行的系列。被認為是執行製作人的馬克·米勒也表示，他相信他們會「之後再回歸」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2021/06/supercrooks-live-action-series-netflix-matt-millar-jupiters-legacy-canceled-cast-released-1234768204/|title='Supercrooks' Live-Action Millarworld Series Ordered By Netflix As 'Jupiter's Legacy' Releases Cast|work=Deadline Hollywood|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|date=June 2, 2021|access-date=June 2, 2021|archive-date=June 2, 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210602220306/https://deadline.com/2021/06/supercrooks-live-action-series-netflix-matt-millar-jupiters-legacy-canceled-cast-released-1234768204/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="Cancellation">{{cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/jupiters-legacy-cancel-netflix-despite-cliffhanger-ending-mark-millar|title=Jupiter's Legacy Canceled at Netflix Despite Cliffhanger Ending|work=IGN|first=J. Kim|last=Murphy|date=June 2, 2021|access-date=June 3, 2021|archive-date=June 3, 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210603014616/https://www.ign.com/articles/jupiters-legacy-cancel-netflix-despite-cliffhanger-ending-mark-millar|url-status=live}}</ref>。預算衝突以及在製作中途用金取代奈特擔任節目統籌是該據決定放棄第二季的一些因素<ref name="CancellationReasons">{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/tv/tv-news/jupiters-legacy-canceled-netflix-season-2-1234965510/|title='Jupiter's Legacy': Battles Over Budgets, Executive Purge Factor in Cancellation|work=The Hollywood Reporter|first=Borys|last=Kit|date=June 11, 2021|accessdate=June 13, 2021|archive-date=June 12, 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210612233918/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/tv/tv-news/jupiters-legacy-canceled-netflix-season-2-1234965510/|url-status=live}}</ref>。

