=== 收視率 ===
《朱比特傳奇》是2021年5月3日至9日這一周內所有[[流媒体|串流媒體]]中收視率最高的節目，根據[[AC尼爾森|AC尼爾森]]的數據，整季的觀看時間為6.96億分鐘。亞軍是《[[侍女的故事_(電視劇)|使女的故事]]》，總時長為6.9億分鐘。 然而，該劇的排名低於Netflix上的一部主要劇集《[[太陽召喚_(電視劇)|太陽召喚]]》的首映場，該劇在上映的周末獲得了7.21億分鐘的收視率<ref>{{cite web|first=Rick|last=Porter|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/tv/tv-news/jupiters-legacy-nielsen-streaming-ratings-1234962632/|title=Canceled ‘Jupiter’s Legacy’ Opens as Top Original Series in Nielsen Streaming Charts|date=June 3, 2021|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|access-date=June 4, 2021|archive-date=June 4, 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210604005347/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/tv/tv-news/jupiters-legacy-nielsen-streaming-ratings-1234962632/|url-status=live}}</ref>。

《朱比特傳奇》在2021年5月10日至16日這一周也位居榜首，觀看時長為10.19億分鐘。緊隨其後的是《{{link-en|創業公司 (電視劇)|StartUp (TV_series)|創業公司}}》，獲得了7.6億分鐘的觀看時間<ref>{{cite web|url=https://kfiam640.iheart.com/content/2021-06-10-netflixs-canceled-jupiters-legacy-tops-streaming-viewership/|title=Netflix's Canceled 'Jupiter's Legacy' Tops Streaming Viewership|date=June 11, 2021|work={{link-en|KFI|KFI}}|access-date=June 12, 2021|archive-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210612044119/https://kfiam640.iheart.com/content/2021-06-10-netflixs-canceled-jupiters-legacy-tops-streaming-viewership/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該劇收視率在5月17日至23日這一周下降了60%，觀看時間為4.05億分鐘。該劇是線上觀看量第三高的{{link-en|原創影集|Original programming}}<ref>{{cite web|first=Rick|last=Porter|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/tv/tv-news/army-of-the-dead-streaming-ratings-may-17-23-1234969716/|title=Zack Snyder's ''Army of the Dead'' Tops Streaming Chart for Debut Weekend|date=June 17, 2021|work=The Hollywood Reporter|access-date=June 18, 2021|archive-date=2021-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210912115043/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/tv/tv-news/army-of-the-dead-streaming-ratings-may-17-23-1234969716/|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，並在包括電影和電視節目在內的收視排名中佔據了第十位<ref>{{cite web|first=Dade|last=Hayes|url=https://deadline.com/2021/06/nielsen-streaming-chart-army-of-the-dead-netflix-1234777655/|title=''Army Of The Dead'' Occupies Top Spot On Nielsen U.S. Streaming Chart|date=June 17, 2021|work=Deadline|access-date=June 18, 2021|archive-date=2021-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814172222/https://deadline.com/2021/06/nielsen-streaming-chart-army-of-the-dead-netflix-1234777655/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在5月24日至30日的一周內，該劇在節目的收視排行榜中排名第7，觀看時長為2.14億分鐘<ref>{{cite web|first=Tyler|last=Hersko|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2021/06/netflix-lucifer-season-5-nielsen-streaming-ratings-1234646785/|title=Netflix's ''Lucifer'' Season 5 Dominates Nielsen's Streaming Ratings|date=June 25, 2021|work=IndieWire|access-date=June 26, 2021|archive-date=2021-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210917154730/https://www.indiewire.com/2021/06/netflix-lucifer-season-5-nielsen-streaming-ratings-1234646785/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

